aan, Caloocan\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/smcentersangandaan/posts/2345968399048168|title=SM Center Sangandaan|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n|-\n|November 3, 2019\n|SM City Bicutan\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/SB19Official/posts/1370069113157555|title=SB19|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n|-\n|November 17, 2019\n|Starmall Alabang\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/SB19Official/posts/1385061741658292|title=SB19|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n|}\n'''For complete list of SB19 Live events, refer here'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/atinundivided/posts/147497386779977|title=SB19 Undivided A'TIN|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n\n<br />\n\n==Awards and Achievements==\n\n<!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:SB19Official.jpg|thumb|right|300px|P-Pop Sensation, SB19]] -->\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!width=\"300\"|Award\n!width=\"50\"|Year\n!width=\"300\"|Recipient(s) and Nominee(s)\n!width=\"300\"|Category\n!width=\"90\"|Result\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| RAWR Awards\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"4\"| SB19\n| align=\"center\"| Favorite Group of the Year\n| {{Won}} \n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lionheartv.net/2019/11/full-list-of-winners-of-the-rawr-awards-2019/|title=FullList Of Winners of the RAWR Awards 2019|date=2019-11-15|website=LionhearTV|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-25}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| PPOP Awards For Young Artist\n| align=\"center\"| Most Favorite POP Boy Group of the Year\n| {{Won}} \n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/PpopArtistsLeague/photos/a.1502173203401147/2507080529577071/?type=3&theater|title=PPOP Awards For Young Artists|date=2019-11-30|website=FB|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-03}}